nodes.text: The New Jedi Order: Edge of Victory I: Conquest (Talking Book Publishers Inc. audiobook)

The New Jedi Order: Edge of Victory I: Conquest is the unabridged audiobook version of the Star Wars Legends novel of the same name, by author Greg Keyes. The audiobook was performed by David Hartley-Margolin and was released by Talking Book Publishers Inc. in 2012.
